-- ANTI-CHEAT: the game now BANS instant CFrame teleports. ALL hub movement goes through flyTo(),
-- which drives the HumanoidRootPart with a BodyVelocity at a capped speed, so the server sees normal
-- continuous motion (a fast "fly") instead of a teleport. Tunable via Misc > Movement > Fly Speed.
-- flyMoveSpeed = 0 means "match the player's real in-game move speed" (Humanoid.WalkSpeed, which
-- pets and speed mushrooms boost) -- the safest setting, since the server sees a legit travel speed.
flyMoveSpeed = 0
